data.description: What a great 4/2/2 home!! Very spacious and wonderfully designed home with lots of natural lighting. Kitchen has gas stove, granite and fridge stays with home. Split bedrooms.  The master bedroom is large with a beautiful double sink bathroom. All the bedrooms are great size.   Need lots of space for kids, gatherings or fur babies? Well this one definitely has just that!  Lots of wonderful space with really nice stamped patios and walkways. Laundry room has extra cabinets and storage and is fantastic size!
